= TTF_MeasureText =

Get the measurement string of text without rendering e.g.

== Syntax ==

<syntaxhighlight lang='c'>
int TTF_MeasureText(TTF_Font *font, const char *text, int measure_width, int *extent, int *count);
</syntaxhighlight>

== Function Parameters ==

{|
|'''font'''
|[[TTF_Font]] handle
|-
|'''text'''
|text to render
|-
|'''measure_width'''
|in pixels to measure this text (input)
|-
|'''count'''
|number of characters that can be rendered (output)
|-
|'''extent'''
|latest calculated width (output)
|}

== Return Value ==

Returns 0 if successful, -1 on error

== Remarks ==

the number of characters that can be rendered before reaching
'measure_width'

